<li><a href="http://www.janes.com/security/law_enforcement/news/jir/jir060717_1_n.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.janes.com/security/law_enforcement/news/jir/jir060717_1_n.shtml" rel="nofollow">Hungary emerges as base for foreign organized crime groups</a> Jane's Intelligence Review, July 2006</li>
<li><a href="http://www.janes.com/security/law_enforcement/news/jir/jir070116_1_n.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.janes.com/security/law_enforcement/news/jir/jir070116_1_n.shtml" rel="nofollow">Organized crime killings shock Ireland</a></li>
</ul>


